description: This file is a header file (.h) defining the interface for the Slap Access Manager Object in the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP) component. It contains function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing the access manager, along with licensing and module description comments.

methods.name: SlapCreateAccessManager
methods.description: Creates the Slap Access Manager object with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: SlapAmoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Slap Access Manager object.

methods.name: SlapAmoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified Slap Access Manager object.

methods.name: SlapAmoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls objects necessary for the Slap Access Manager object.

methods.name: SlapAmoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Slap Access Manager object.
